caption:
Welcoming the Spring Equinox with reflection, renewal, and balance. ✨ As the seasons shift, so do we—embracing the harmony of light and dark, releasing what no longer serves us, and making space for new energy. We welcomed in the spring season with a sound bath lead by @jessicastone_co + @jennarainey in the @theecologycenter peace dome. A lovely group of women gathered to reset, recharge, detox, and reconnect with our inner rhythms. Here’s to aligning mind, body, and spirit for the season ahead.
